  Kinetic (Delta T^0):                   1.046284903395383         28.4709           656.55          2747.02
  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.634737271854593        -17.2721          -398.30         -1666.50
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.236747816652351         -6.4422          -148.56          -621.58
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.066710548808587          1.8153            41.86           175.15
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.037190083191629         -1.0120           -23.34           -97.64
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.204320280505396          5.5598           128.21           536.44
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

